    "body" : "<p>If you're having problems related to dependencies not appearing in the WEB-INF/lib file when running on a Tomcat server in Eclipse, take a look at this:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4777026/classnotfoundexception-dispatcherservlet-when-launching-tomcat-maven-dependencie\">ClassNotFoundException DispatcherServlet when launching Tomcat (Maven dependencies not copied to wtpwebapps)</a></p>\n\n<p>You simply had to add the Maven Dependencies in Project Properties > Deployment Assembly.</p>\n"
  }, {
